Fortis has 85 000 employees and is one of the twenty largest banks in Europe and the ten largest insurers.
"It is not lost money," said Dutch Finance Minister Wouter Bos yesterday.
In return, influence and voting rights are gained in banking matters.
It is certainly something that savers and families appreciate now that the times are unsure "
