The accusations that the magistrates of Calabria's Anti-Mafia Directorate are making to the mayor and deputy mayor of Gioia Tauro Giorgio Dal Torrione and Rosario Schiavone, and to the mayor of Rosarno Carlo Martelli, arrested this morning for external competition in Mafia association, are heavy.
In handcuffs also Gioacchino Piroballi, the elderly mediator between the clan and the public administrations, and his nephew lawyer, namesake of the boss, already condemned for association for criminals of mafia type, condemned to compensate 10 million euros.
